NODE-SELECTOR
----------------
Why node selector?
Actually by default sheduler will deside to create pod
but i want to take the chance to create in specific worker node
that why we have create label for wokernode use that we have to add node selecetor
if there is no enough resources for selected node?
it will o for pending stage
->kubectl label nodes i-1223r3wttwtysy node=worker1
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: mypod-1
  labels:
    app: frontend
spec:
  nodeSelector:
    node: worker1
  containers:
    - name: mycont-1
      image: shaikmustafa/dm
      ports:
        - containerPort: 80

